Title: ICT Management and Leadership Conference 2023
Description: Technology is vital for every Australian school. The rich integration of different technologies is needed to ensure a seamless experience for all users. ICT education professionals know the value of understanding the latest opportunities, the imminent threats and the importance of continuous learning.
